name: Little Basil Bunny Set
description:
Little Basil Bunny is made from a mix of Minky and 100% designer cotton Fabric. He is stuffed with Innergreens' 100% corn fibre toy filling, it has been voted as the best toy filler on the market. The fibre is extremely soft whilst maintaining its shape and resilience. The fibre also holds a very low flammability rating. It is also naturally hypoallergenic & Anti-bacterial

His body is about 18cm tall and wide (this does not include his ears or arms and legs)

So cute and soft this set includes Bunny, matching easter egg and carrot as well as a little plastic egg to fill with an extra special suprise!!

I have tried to make this as safe as possible for the little ones but please remember to check and supervise under 3's.

This listing does not include the basket or chocolate easter eggs.

Postage is for regular mail only, I cannot be responsible for parcels that aren't registered. Please select express or registered mail before you check out.
